      <title>敦促尼日利亚取消对抗议者可能判处的死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nigeria-urged-to-drop-possible-death-sentence-against-protesters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人权观察组织敦促尼日利亚撤销对上个月反政府示威活动中拘留的抗议者的叛国罪指控，该指控可能被判处死刑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nigeria-urged-to-drop-possible-death-sentence-against-protesters</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:06:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国提议阻止中国在非洲建立军事基地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-pitches-deal-to-thwart-chinese-military-base-in-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国正在为加蓬制定一项经济和安全援助计划，以阻止中国在这个具有战略地位的中非国家建立军事足迹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-pitches-deal-to-thwart-chinese-military-base-in-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 15:04:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加速退出煤炭市场的计划可能激怒波兰政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/plan-to-speed-up-coal-exit-risks-roiling-polish-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰气候部正在大力推动退出煤炭市场，此举可能会激怒矿工，并在明年总统大选前引发执政联盟内部新的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/plan-to-speed-up-coal-exit-risks-roiling-polish-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:32:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列和哈马斯坚持立场 美国仍在推动加沙停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-still-pushing-gaza-cease-fire-deal-as-israel-and-hamas-dig-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大约三个月前，美国总统乔·拜登表示，以色列和哈马斯面临“决定性时刻”，当时他提议达成停火协议，以暂停他们在加沙的毁灭性战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/us-still-pushing-gaza-cease-fire-deal-as-israel-and-hamas-dig-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 13:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国特派团建议向饱受战争蹂躏的苏丹部署维和部队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/un-mission-recommends-peacekeepers-be-deployed-in-war-torn-sudan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国苏丹实况调查团建议国际社会部署一支独立的军事力量，保护平民免遭“令人悲惨的侵犯人权行为和国际犯罪”的侵害。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/un-mission-recommends-peacekeepers-be-deployed-in-war-torn-sudan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国新政府在政治混乱后宣誓就职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/thailand-s-new-government-sworn-in-after-bout-of-political-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国新任总理巴东丹·西那瓦及其内阁于周五宣誓就职，这意味着泰国政府可以在东南亚国家陷入政治动荡之后开始开展工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/thailand-s-new-government-sworn-in-after-bout-of-political-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:27:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国同意拯救邮轮制造商 Meyer Werft</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/germany-reaches-rescue-deal-for-cruise-ship-builder-meyer-werft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国达成了一项协议，为陷入困境的造船商迈尔造船厂有限公司 (Meyer Werft GmbH) 提供了潜在的救命稻草，这家私营公司最近赢得了为迪士尼邮轮公司船队提供船只的后续合同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/germany-reaches-rescue-deal-for-cruise-ship-builder-meyer-werft</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:58:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚与卡车司机达成协议，结束严重的道路封锁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/colombia-reaches-deal-with-truckers-to-end-crippling-road-blocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚政府与卡车司机达成协议，将柴油价格上调幅度控制在低于计划的水平，从而结束了已进入第五天、几乎令全国陷入瘫痪的罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/colombia-reaches-deal-with-truckers-to-end-crippling-road-blocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:54:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普还是哈里斯？普京的偏好并不明确</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/trump-or-harris-for-putin-the-choice-isn-t-so-clear-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早在 2016 年，弗拉基米尔·普京就是特朗普的支持者。11 月 9 日凌晨，克里姆林宫高层官员打开香槟庆祝这位商人出身的政治家在美国大选中意外获胜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/trump-or-harris-for-putin-the-choice-isn-t-so-clear-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:12:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Petro 解决了哥伦比亚的一场危机，其他危机即将到来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/colombia-trucker-strike-is-gustavo-petro-s-biggest-social-crisis-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[古斯塔沃·佩特罗于 2022 年上台，承诺改善数千万哥伦比亚穷人的生活。两年后，受腐败丑闻、内阁不断更替和改革失败的困扰，他本周面临总统任期内最大的社会危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/colombia-trucker-strike-is-gustavo-petro-s-biggest-social-crisis-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 02:20:47 GMT</pubDate>
